<POST>
<POSTER> maps.huge.info </POSTER>
<POSTDATE> 2005-08-26T24:02:00 </POSTDATE>

&lt;body onload=&quot;onLoad();&quot;&gt;

Caveat: DO NOT NAME the function onload() as that will cause a real
headache. Just call it anything else. onLoad is ok because it is case
sensitive.

-John


